## Tech Stack

- **Server:** Express.js (TypeScript)
- **Client:** React 18 + Vite
- **Styling:** TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui
- **Database:** PostgreSQL + Drizzle ORM
- **API Layer:** React Query + centralized fetch client

