## Rules

1. Run `npm run build && npx tsc --noEmit && npm test` before every push
2. Check generated SQL before running migrations - no DROP TABLE/COLUMN
3. Keep primary UI above the fold
4. Server must listen on `0.0.0.0` for deployment compatibility
